title: Rachel Rising, Volume 2: Fear No Malus
description: Rachel and Jet are dead. So why are they still here, looking drop dead gorgeous? Zoe, a 10-year old serial killer, suggests the answer is Lilith, an ethereal woman who seeks to destroy the town that hung them for witchcraft over 300 years ago. But Zoe is full of surprises, including an indwelling demon named Malus with his own wicked plan reaching far beyond the city limits. The only thing standing in his way is... Rachel. Collects #7-12.
author: Terry Moore
